Package: soc504replication
Title: Replication Workflow for Best et al. (2023)
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Vivek V Adury", family = "User", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Standalone, script-based replication workflow for the main analysis
